{"lemma":"حُرْقَةُ","slug":"حُرْقَةُ","root":"ح.ر.ق","root_slug":"ح-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7703","n7704","n7711","n7712","n7713"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a burn; an instance of burning","tags":["colloquial"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a burning sensation (at a particular site of the body)","tags":["colloquial"],"examples":[{"text":"حَرْقَة في البول","english":"a burning sensation in the urine"},{"text":"حَرْقَة في المَعِدَة","english":"heartburn, acid reflux"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from حَرَقَ (ḥaraqa, “to burn”)."},"ipa":["/ħar.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7703","headword_ar":"حَرَقَهُ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqN","text_ar":"حَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haraqahu","text_ar":"حَرَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqN","text_ar":"حَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filed it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he rubbed one part of it with another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haraqa naAbahu","text_ar":"حَرَقَ نَابَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ground his dog-tooth, so that it made a grating sound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) when said of a stallion-camel, denoting threatening: and, accord. to IDrd, when the like is said of a she-camel, it is asserted to denote a consequence of fatigue. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^asonaAna","text_ar":"الاَسْنَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~aqa","text_ar":"حَرَّقَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEZ","text_ar":"رعظ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He grated the teeth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in that art.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yaHoruqu Ealayoka","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَحْرُقُ عَلَيْكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ur~ama gayoZFA","text_ar":"الاُرَّمَ غَيْظًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one grinds together the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ar~m","text_ar":"ارّم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"molar teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as the word is generally understood to mean in this case, but other meanings are assigned to it,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in anger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rage"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like one filing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^uz~ama","text_ar":"الاُزَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the canine teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and the verb is also used without the objective complement, because the meaning is understood. (Ham p. 115.) IDrd makes the act to be that of the canine tooth; saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haraqa naAbu AlbaEiyri","text_ar":"حَرَقَ نَابُ البَعِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The canine tooth of the camel made a grating sound."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) AHát also mentions the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yaHoruqu naAbuhu EalaY~a","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَحْرُقُ نَابُهُ عَلَىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one's canine tooth makes a grating sound at me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and Zuheyr uses the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHoruqu naAbuhu","text_ar":"يَحْرُقُ نَابُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham p. 286.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqN","text_ar":"حَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eating to the uttermost."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haruqa","text_ar":"حَرُقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, evil in disposition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraqN","text_ar":"حَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as an inf. n., [i. e. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqa","text_ar":"حَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies A garment's, or cloth's,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being burnt by beating"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with too much violence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (KL.) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"springing forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shooting forth, vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of lightning. (KL.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqa $aEaruhu","text_ar":"حَرِقَ شَعَرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraqN","text_ar":"حَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His hair fell off piecemeal."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqati AlnaASiyapu","text_ar":"حَرِقَتِ النَاصِيَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The forelock"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became thin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scanty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaraqu","text_ar":"الحَرَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nASyp","text_ar":"ناصية"},{"kind":"text","text":"is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~afaA","text_ar":"السَّفَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqati All~iHoyapu","text_ar":"حَرِقَتِ اللِّحْيَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beard was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, shorter upon the chin than upon the two sides of the face."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqa","text_ar":"حَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraqN","text_ar":"حَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAriqap","text_ar":"حَارِقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a man: in speaking of a camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huriqa","text_ar":"حُرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuniYa","text_ar":"عُنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is more commonly used than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqa","text_ar":"حَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n7704","headword_ar":"حرّقهُ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoriyqN","text_ar":"تَحْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHryq","text_ar":"تحريق"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies Fire's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making a mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impression, upon a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr~q AlA_ibila","text_ar":"حرّق الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of pasturage, (K,) [particularly] of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It made the camels thirsty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A2-  See also 1."}],"source_refs":["K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n7711","headword_ar":"حَرْقَةٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7712","headword_ar":"حُرْقَةٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[A state of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotaraqa","text_ar":"اِحْتَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariyqN","text_ar":"حَرِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) Thus the latter means in the Kur [lxxxv. 10], ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa lahumo Ea*aAbu AlHariyqi","text_ar":"وَ لَهُمْ عَذَابُ الحَرِيقِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And for them"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the punishment of burning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in other passages in the Kur]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A burning such as a man experiences from the taste of a thing in which is heat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from love,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grief;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is experienced in the eye from ophthalmia,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the heart from pain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY jawofihi HuroqapN","text_ar":"فِى جَوْفِهِ حُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest, is heat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqapN","text_ar":"حَرْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariyqapN","text_ar":"حَرِيقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n7713","headword_ar":"حُرَقَةٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariqN","text_ar":"حَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}